 !''!'
    M.I @:FIU1 FI U2
    Q0"G Q0M(M.M&_CHAR PRINT) FT_'
    Q2-*"N			    !* IF HE WANTS SPECIFIC SUBCOMMAND,!
       F~4.Z"E			    !* If dispatch is ^\, flush CR!
	 FI'			    !* (C108 only)!
       FQ3/5-Q2"G Q:3(Q2)' "# 0'"E  !* If char is not defined, upcase it.!
